User.create(username: "Bruce_Lee", nickname: "小龙", password: "brucelee", hometown: "San Francisco", age: 15, reach: 68, weight: 64, height: 175, bio: "Don't get set into one form, adapt it and build your own, and let it grow, be like water. Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless — like water. Now you put water in a cup, it becomes the cup; You put water into a bottle it becomes the bottle; You put it in a teapot it becomes the teapot. Now water can flow or it can crash. Be water, my friend.", img_url: '/public/assets/p1.jpg')
User.create(username: "Rocky_Balboa", password: "rockybalboa", nickname: "The Italian Stallion", hometown: "Philly", age: 63, reach: 78, weight: 81, height: 170, bio: "Let me tell you something you already know. The world ain't all sunshine and rainbows. It's a very mean and nasty place and I don't care how tough you are, it will beat you to your knees and keep you there permanently if you let it. You, me, or nobody is gonna hit as hard as life. But it ain't about how hard ya hit. It's about how hard you can get hit and keep moving forward. How much you can take and keep moving forward. That's how winning is done!", img_url: '/public/assets/p2.jpg')
User.create(username: "Conor_McGregor", password: "conormcgregor", nickname: "The Notorious", weight: 72, height: 176, img_url: '/public/assets/p3.jpg', hometown: "Dublin", age: 27, reach: 74, bio: "There's no talent here, this is hard work. This is an obsession. Talent does not exist, we are all equal as human beings. You could be anyone if you put in the time. You will reach the top, and that's that. I am not talented, I am obsessed.")
User.create(username: "Bruce_Wayne", password: "brucewayne", nickname: "Certainly not Batman, lol... Why would you even think that?", hometown: "Gotham City", age: 42, reach: 77, weight: 108, height: 186, img_url: '/public/assets/p4.jpg', bio: "They told me there was nothing out there, nothing to fear. But the night my parents were murdered I caught a glimpse of something. I've looked for it ever since. I went around the world, searched in all the shadows. And there is something out there in the darkness, something terrifying, something that will not stop until it gets revenge... Me.")
